/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Marsala\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/108\">Museo archeologico regionale Lilibeo Marsala - Baglio Anselmi\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\">6649\u003C/idno>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"la\">Latin\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>A limestone tympanum from a small aedicola. The left and right ends of the tympanum have been sawn off at a later date (the block was re-used as a threshold in a mediaeval structure. The upper and lower cornice have been damaged. The inscription runs below the lower cornice. The framed pediment of the tympanum is empty.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.limestone\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html\">limestone\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.arch_element.tympanum\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/1951.html\">tympanum\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--silvestrini-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">49\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">108\u003C/width>\n                       